## Leaflet: Adding Polygons{.smaller}
<hr>
Specify a color scale for your polygons with `fillColor`.


```{r}
#| code-line-numbers: "|3-7|4|5|6|"
#| eval: false
leaflet(data = world) |>
  addTiles() |>
  addPolygons(
    fillColor = topo.colors(10, alpha = NULL),
    stroke = FALSE,
    label = ~ name
  )
```


